---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The coursework, explained" active="task">
  <div class="part-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="kicker">The assessment</p>
      <h1>The coursework, explained</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="band">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p>One assignment on Macbeth for the Edexcel International GCSE English Literature coursework component, marked on AO1 (knowledge, critical style, personal engagement) and AO2 (language, form and structure). Open book, drafted over weeks, and governed by strict integrity rules: the essay must be entirely the student's own work, AI must not write or edit any of it, and plagiarism means disqualification. Because of those rules there is no AI feedback tool on this site. Full question guidance, planning scaffolds and the drafting timeline will appear here alongside the guides.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
